I love Marvin Sapp, don't get me wrong.  I play his c.d.'s over and over and over.  So much that I thought what better than to see him sing live.. I know this is gospel but Marvin brings nothing to his stage performance.  The Rev. James Moore was a joy to watch on video even in his latter years when he was going blind.  Sorry, but Marvin has no stage presence.

I have been a Marvin Sapp fan for many years, and once again, this DVD is a wonderful addition to my musical collection. His music is beautiful and inspiring, and his performances will lead you into worship as you watch him worship in this recording!  Awesome man of God...I've been blessed by his ministry!
Great, that's all I can say. Good picture quality, music is excellent, Calvin is ripping as usual.... JUst buy it!!!
Great service the DVD arrived early.  In wonderful condition.  Unfortunately I meant to order the CD but I gave it to a friend.  That was my mistake.  Now I will order the CD.
